CODE QUALITY REVIEWER PROMPT TEMPLATE
Use this template when dispatching a code quality reviewer subagent. 
Purpose: Verify implementation is well-built (clean, tested, maintainable) 
Only dispatch after spec compliance review passes. 
CODE  290CHARS
In addition to standard code quality concerns, the reviewer should check: 
Does each file have one clear responsibility with a well-defined interface? Are units decomposed so they can be understood and tested independently? IT implementation following the file structure from the plan? Did this implementation create new files that are already large, or significantly grow existing files? (Don't flag pre-existing file sizes — focus on what this change contributed.) 
Code reviewer returns: Strengths, Issues (Critical/Important/Minor), Assessment 